    'isi2' => '<h6 id="toc-0">Recipe for Tamarind Ice Drink</h6>
    <h6 id="toc-1">Javanese Tamarind Ice Drink Ingredients</h6>
    <ul><li>200 grams of real tamarind</li><li>1 liter of water</li><li>sugar to taste</li></ul>
    <h6 id="toc-2">How to Make Tamarind Ice Drink </h6>
    <ol><li>We first prepare the tamarind then clean it, and after that we cut it according to our taste</li><li>then turn on the stove over medium heat, prepare the pot and add the chopped tamarind into it, wait until the tamarind boils</li><li>after boiling we let it sit for about 7 minutes, reduce the stove heat</li><li>then take it out and let it cool for a while until it is really cold</li>< li>sieve the tamarind with a sieve and remove any remaining lumps</li><li>add some sugar</li><li>put it in the freezer</li><li>wait until frozen and ready to serve</li><li>Recipe for Es Sari Tamarind Drink.</li></ol>
    <p>Well, that a very delicious and warm ice drink recipe, and there are many more, you know that are even tastier than the recipe above, good luck.</p>
    <p>Recipe Source : https://www.resepumiku.com/2016/06/resep-cara-membuat-minuman-es-sari-asam.html</p>',
