    'isi23' => '<p>Javanese acid has a lot of content and nutritional value for the human body. Why do many herbs and traditional medicine use<a href="https://asamjawagunung.com"> tamarind</a>? The answer is because tamarind is one of the original Indonesian crops which has many benefits and high nutritional value and is able to treat various ailments. If you want to know what the content and nutritional value of tamarind is, this article will provide the information.</p>
