    'isi25' => '<p>Tea is a very common drink. Almost all places to eat provide this drink. Easy to make, delicious, cheap and refreshing, that`s why tea is quite a fan in various parts of the world. There are also many variations of making tea, and one of the delicious drink variants served hot or cold is sparkling tamarind tea. A tea drink but with a fresh tamarind taste. Hmm, must be appetizing huh? What is special is that this tea is made with a mixture of selected ingredients, namely using Tamarind Cap Gunung which has guaranteed taste and quality. How? You want to try it too? Let`s look at the following recipe.</p>
