    'isi26' => '<p>Hearing a food called a burger, it must be familiar to you. Although this food is not authentic Indonesian food, burgers can be easily enjoyed everywhere. Even in elementary schools though. This time we present a Turkish-style burger recipe that uses tamarind ingredients. Curious what the recipe is like? Here it is!</p>
