    'isi27' => '<p>Inji Puli, his name may be foreign to our ears as Indonesians. But if you are a lover of Indian food and often visit Indian restaurants in the country, you may know him. This dish is seasoned with spicy spices and is a type of side sauce that is usually served with warm rice. If you are still curious about the shape and taste, how about you make it yourself at home? Here are the ingredients, spices and how to make it:</p>
