    'isi33' => '<h6>The Enjoyment of Homemade Asem Vegetables Using Tamarind Cap Gunung</h6>
    <p>Sayur tamarind is a typical Indonesian vegetable that you can easily find in many homes. If you are a lover of home cooking, you must be familiar with the name Sayur Asem. As the name suggests, vegetable tamarind does taste sour and there is a sweet and savory sensation in the sauce. The sour taste obtained from vegetable tamarind is a combination of tamarind which is put into boiling gravy along with other spices and ingredients. If you are curious and want to try this dish at home, here we include the recipe for you.</p>
